---
title: Smart Blueberry-Dressed Chicken Thighs Salad with Almond Pralines
description: This summery salad is simple and tasty any time of year! Mixed greens are tossed with a stellar blueberry vinaigrette, while pan-fried chicken brings a filling protein hit. Plus, who can say no to sweet and crunchy almond pralines to top things off?!

